"hkgmoji\" />仲可以成功令到同路人做靶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其他嘉年華人士只係用把口屌"},{"pid":"829997ab80fd0887f594705258a599e32dd65837","tid":1308902,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:21:01.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0aaf5cf3276d3c726359c787c5a0c89c7624d8e","tid":1308902,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8548ae409f0709f91ca9e3d404d1a2bb96e57b3","tid":1308902,"uid":139732,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:21:43.000Z","msg":"認同,不過真心覺得唔需要去守,撕一貼百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b5c2364900a1959a4dd605c96fc1baa636fdf5","tid":1308902,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:22:09.000Z","msg":"[突發][713光復上水]一封北區居民寫給香港人的公開信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307753</a><br />\n<br />\n！！緊 急 ！！突 發！！上 水 連 儂 牆 要 人！ ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308369</a><br />\n<br />\n［抗爭支線］！七 月 十 三 ！光 復 上 水 ！踢 走 水 貨 客！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307559</a>"},{"pid":"a4dba1d42cd80e9ed34fc56fceca70d458fcf244","tid":1308902,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:22:22.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beca3cdbc2dd22ddd9292daa112e5aada4228d54","tid":1308902,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"