replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:25:09.000Z","msg":"連儂牆, 只貼不守"},{"pid":"31df94c28a14854131545cc232ebe027fcb40beb","tid":1308902,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:25:13.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589d4e3eacce3d406d2568992547537054ace36f","tid":1308902,"uid":33471,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"有用 但塊牆既祖先都係由得人搞 第二日又再黎過 象徵著你阻唔到發達言論既自由<br />\n而唔係死守 浪費人力物力 又俾機會廢老搞事 你還手定唔還手<br />\n說好的撕一貼百呢"},{"pid":"8b179ac9db1ac1088dd54ac9c971fad6d780aeb6","tid":1308902,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"堅持自己做嘅事<br />\n各有各做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實大家只係心急<br />\n成個連登冇乜點宣傳到黎緊嘅行動<br />\n令到好多人唔知行動資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我嘅睇法係連儂牆可以照做，但唔洗開咁多post<br />\n連登應該多返啲行動post，上返熱門<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P66PjK1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP66PjK1.jpg&h=85e659f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1a43cfb8b78d3ad5dbf1386067529c2952293bb","tid":1308902,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921bae8022d6bf18104552f59a0e06e34fe429c5","tid":1308902,"uid":262187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:26:21.000Z","msg":"當同藍絲有衝突個陣，如果我地自己人處理得好，其實可以好好咁突顯我地嘅文明，打擊對家嘅野蠻，亦都係拉攏多D人過黎我地個邊嘅好機會(所以我太唔建議有衝突個陣還手，制服包圍就好，一黎有法律風險，二黎智取會比力取好)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個就13拳, 隨時比人打到頸椎都斷<br />\n另一個就比人打到臂骨都斷<br />\n<br />\n和理非既人血饅頭真係好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地有權力有武力, 居然走黎講&quot;智取&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次有人行出黎制服, 成班左膠就拿拿聲話唔好打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地撕完走, 又無人夠膽阻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c765a767a26757de09e7ca1e834813060fa1f475","tid":1308902,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:26:28.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277004283696d26dd8a500ec185dae1c64029fc4","tid":1308902,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"唔洗灰心呀樓豬<br />\n忠於自己，做合乎公義的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做連儂牆之餘得閒上連登推下行動post<br />\n或者靠你地係連儂牆貼上宣傳海報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c518e9a8c668d6043d13dec55aca6516427ace7","tid":1308902,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"921bae8022d6bf18104552f59a0e06e34fe429c5","tid":1308902,"uid":262187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:26:21.000Z","msg":"當同藍絲有衝突個陣，如果我地自己人處理得好，其實可以好好咁突顯我地嘅文明，打擊對家嘅野蠻，亦都係拉攏多D人過黎我地個邊嘅好機會(所以我太唔建議有衝突個陣還手，制服包圍就好，一黎有法律風險，二黎智取會比力取好)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\